 safe for so many years. You have to stay alert and understand what the townsfolk are saying. You have to figure out who could have possibly done such a horrible act and doom the village. Emerge in this town, become its member and save the town. ", "short_description": "The clock is ticking and only three hours remain until the sun devours Arkala town. It is up to you to put on a cape and save these people. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.1neglakay.com/tomorrowends", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Kadanss Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.1neglakay.com/tomorrowends", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "500276661658227"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974883_638856910759031_6930865527422337670_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_i4LbgZvRW4Q7kNvgF0_pL0&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARj7M1RaVzFr9Qgn2TFXB1a&oh=00_AYCggYX9UkS8kfoZV9tFdxzFAIPoxP2_tsvjTw2a3EYShg&oe=66E80166"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Tomorrow Ends", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1647662400, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "295906192559420", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_me